snippet.title: DJ Semtex interview with Lancey Fouxx; Working with Kanye West, Skepta, Lil Yachty, & loads more
snippet.description:
I've witnessed Lancey Fouxx start from the bottom and work his way up. He figured the game out early, knew what he wanted, never stopped, never looked back, and constantly put in the work. 
He just dropped his 9th body of work LIVE.EVIL and he has the next 10 projects mapped out. He's a special artist who will be as big in music as he will in fashion. This is my first ever interview with Lancey Fouxx.

LiVE.EVIL out now 

Catch DJ Semtex live on Capital Xtra every Friday From 9pm.

#LanceyFouxx #DJSemtex #CapitalXtra
